text: Karin Elisabeth Westman (born 17 May 1966) is a road cyclist from Sweden. She represented her nation at the 1992 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:Swedish female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Sweden Category:Living people Category:People from Västerås Category:1966 births
